Class RTS_PROCEDURE

java.lang.Object

simula.runtime.RTS_PROCEDURE
public abstract class RTS_PROCEDURE extends RTS_BASICIO

Utility class PROCEDURE.

This class is used as prefix to all java classes representing Simula Procedures.
